*Oče* je naučio njegovog sina da pliva. (His father taught his son to swim.)

Ona je svojim *očevima* obećala da će se pobrinuti za sestru. (She promised her parents that she would take care of her sister.)

On je često slušao savjete svojih *očeva*. (He often listened to the advice of his fathers.)

*Očevi* su posjetili svoje unuke. (The fathers visited their grandchildren.)

Oni su svi zajedno proslavili *očev* dane. (They all celebrated Father's Day together.)